{"tid":1764843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「後果自負」珠海公安千人在港珠澳大橋反恐演練　港警高層出席","createTime":"2019-12-01T12:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T01:22:27.000Z","uid":73915,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2b1b923d7a8c00bb07b41ed027529e535a0dd708","tid":1764843,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1495374_2_20191201114354.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1495374_2_20191201114354.jpg&h=e72b6cd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n珠海市公安局前日在港珠澳大橋珠海公路口岸，舉行反恐應急、處理突發情況演練。香港警務處副處長蕭澤頤、澳門警察總局局長助理吳錦華等人出席。<br />\n<br />\n內地網站報道，珠海公安集結1000多名警力、80多輛警車參加，分為警力集結、技能展示、反恐處突和集體宣誓四部分，針對暴力手段、對抗程度等情況，演練攔截隊形、加強隊形，以及支援、防禦、推進、抓捕技術動作。<br />\n<br />\n108名基層民警聯合演練棍盾攻防術，結合伸縮警棍和圓盾使用，展現止暴制亂的單兵作戰能力。交警摩托車滾動護衛隊展示蛇形繞樁、對向穿插繞樁等駕駛技能；特警演練警用無人機與「黑飛」無人機的空中對抗反制戰術。<br />\n<br />\n市委書記、市人大常委會主任郭永航強調，確保在任何時候、任何情況下都堅決聽黨話、跟黨走，要忠誠履行職責使命，為推進粵港澳大灣區建設、迎接澳門回歸祖國20周年創造平安穩定的政治社會環境。"},{"pid":"5531016c16cd7922992285fcb3eadb9cec313922","tid":1764843,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"突擊香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54410a10a7a34ca33a53bc1c49e621cbd5c637b1","tid":1764843,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:06:01.000Z","msg":"好撚驚呀 出未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec773c0d06a298479dfba6248e85f74cdf900ae2","tid":1764843,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:06:23.000Z","msg":"練完好番去摺被啦<br />\n個個笑鳩你地一日練到黑又唔打真軍<br />\n咁演練我都勁過飛虎啦<br />\n張圖個盾陣左右都真空無擋想點姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f32e33bf084f9e10bf50974d6174891e8d1762b","tid":1764843,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:07:04.000Z","msg":"大陸顧掂自己先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c913099dcbc0ce189486c55860d014c6f24051","tid":1764843,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"港警高層物色武警加入香港警隊<br />\n入境處特快批核"},{"pid":"3683e9e450838667ecf11de37d1cffb8966ec327","tid":1764843,"uid":270619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs2.imagebam.com/cb/a5/3d/d3a86c1322024035.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs2.imagebam.com%2Fcb%2Fa5%2F3d%2Fd3a86c1322024035.jpg&h=c5280c6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3896b4fa213f3e7596d2b8dd08ec95e226b33f53","tid":1764843,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:24:34.000Z","msg":"班支那豬應該係拎去嚇澳門<br />\n香港已經打到飛起仲使你擺陣嚇咩"},{"pid":"0be26e2a09568dc568c84c5b28fc35b8495e5601","tid":1764843,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3896b4fa213f3e7596d2b8dd08ec95e226b33f53","tid":1764843,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:24:34.000Z","msg":"班支那豬應該係拎去嚇澳門<br />\n香港已經打到飛起仲使你擺陣嚇咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5bb7d705f5419ff7b9219ea09bb556371761af","tid":1764843,"uid":2113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"即係嗰所謂1000退休警？"},{"pid":"39d94c146ac382a8a077f5b7716da3b03cecd0b7","tid":1764843,"uid":261677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:41:02.000Z","msg":"做比邊個睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76401b802852658feb5fcdd3180db2db17ae043c","tid":1764843,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci